thuanian"},{"language":"mt","lang_name":"Maltese"},{"language":"se","lang_name":"Sami"},{"language":"pap","lang_name":"Papiamento"},{"language":"med","lang_name":"Melpa"}]},{"phelps":"BH11209","text":"Gee Kayne dah mah zon, Ke shay Manito, che ke kayne ne me nan, Shegwah che mah wim we to nan, Che mean e ge e ze yan. Che ke kayne ne me nan ke kaye da ma zon ke zong e ze win she quah neen aye pee chee nay. sou e ze yan, shegwa ka a pe chee we note e ze yun. She gwah neen apee chee ke tee mak e ze anne. Keen aye ta go ka Manito win, ka we che tas so win, Apee saig e ze an, kah ke kay kah ah ya yin.\n\n* I bear witness, O my God, that Thou hast created me to know Thee and to worship Thee. I testify, at this moment, to my powerlessness and to Thy might, to my poverty and to Thy wealth.\nThere is none other God but Thee, the Help in Peril, the Self-Subsisting.","name":"Short Obligatory Prayer","category":"Saulteaux","order_in_cat":1,"source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"58a866f9-f971-4322-8161-25a628eab906","v":"58ye18dh9io77zyuijg5hxtl2","book_cats":{"af:bp":{"cat":"Kort verpligte gebed","order_in_cat":1},"am:bp":{"cat":"አጭሩ (Short)","order_in_cat":1},"ar:bp":{"cat":"الصلاة   الصغيرة","order_in_cat":1},"az:bp":{"cat":"Qısa Namaz","order_in_cat":1},"be:bp":{"cat":"Кароткая абавязковая малітва","order_in_cat":1},"bg:bp":{"cat":"Кратка задължителна молитва","order_in_cat":1},"bi:bp":{"cat":"SOTFALA  OBLIGATORI  PREA","order_in_cat":1},"bs:bp":{"cat":"Kratka Obavezna Molitva","order_in_cat":1},"ca:bp":{"cat":"Oració obligatòria curta","order_in_cat":1},"co:bp":{"cat":"Preghera dì tutti i ghjorni","order_in_cat":1},"cs:bp":{"cat":"Krátká denní modlitba","order_in_cat":1},"cy:bp":{"cat":"Short Obligatory Prayer","order_in_cat":1},"da:bp":{"cat":"Kort Obligatorisk Bøn","order_in_cat":1},"de:bp":{"cat":"Das kurze Pflichtgebet","order_in_cat":1},"dgz:bp":{"cat":"Marek Iyanupe U’uraewa (Short Obligatory Prayer)","order_in_cat":1},"el:bp":{"cat":"ΜΙΚΡΗ ΥΠΟΧΡΕΩΤΙΚΗ ΠΡΟΣΕΥΧΗ","orde